author: kfogel
msg: Make some infrastructure improvements in the test suite, in
preparation for r14572, which depends on them.
* subversion/tests/clients/cmdline/svntest/actions.py
(match_or_fail): New helper, does regexp matching.
(display_lines): New parameter 'expected_is_regexp', conditionally
adjust display accordingly.  Document.
(run_and_verify_svn): If 'expected' parameter is a string, treat it
as a regexp to match.  Abstract duplicated code into nested function
handle_output.  Fix error message.
